        "cultivation": "Grow in a heated glasshouse where temperatures fall no lower than 13\u00b0C (55\u00b0F) in winter. Use a loam-based compost such as John Innes No 2 in containers or in the glass house border. In the growing season, water moderately and apply a balanced liquid fertiliser monthly. In winter, less water is required. A position in full light, but shaded from hot sun is ideal",
